&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect II | Bellevue, WA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About American Capital Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in Bellevue, Washington in 1987, American Capital Group stands proud as a leader in real estate development. With over three decades of dedicated service, our expertise shines in the realm of multifamily community development. To date, we have crafted over 100 multifamily properties across twelve states, managing 25+ of these properties in four Western states.&lt;/p&gt;
